From: Yicong Yang <yangyicong@hisilicon.com>
Date: Fri, 25 Apr 2025 11:38:45 +0800
Subject: perf mem: Count L2 HITM for c2c statistic
Git-commit: fa9b3578ed628641504ab74958bbe36a42c2615a
Patch-mainline: v6.16-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update

L2 HITM is not counted in c2c statistic decoding. Count it for lcl_hitm
like how we handle L2 Peer snoop.

Reviewed-by: Leo Yan <leo.yan@arm.com>
Signed-off-by: Yicong Yang <yangyicong@hisilicon.com>
Cc: CaiJingtao <caijingtao@huawei.com>
